  "detailed_description": "FROG CORNER is a first person horror game, with found footage stylization<br>The game relies mostly on creating heavy atmosphere, instead of a cheap jump scares.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/20624973bd07a0b5193be1b67df065f4.poster.avif?t=1773853995\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/20624973bd07a0b5193be1b67df065f4.webm?t=1773853995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/20624973bd07a0b5193be1b67df065f4.mp4?t=1773853995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game tells you a story about a person who goes to an abandoned arcade, going deeper and deeper, searching for the mythical arcade machine \"Frog Corner\".<br>And the deeper you go, everything gets even weirder than before.<br>What is \"Frog Corner\"? Why the arcade was abandoned?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Creepy atmosphere </li><li>Clever puzzles </li><li>Unique Style</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/34ef14f2d5966abec22b72de329c0f32.poster.avif?t=1773853995\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/34ef14f2d5966abec22b72de329c0f32.webm?t=1773853995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861020/extras/34ef14f2d5966abec22b72de329c0f32.mp4?t=1773853995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
